headline: Janus Henderson Enterprise Fund Q3 2025 Portfolio Performance
summary: Among individual holdings, CarMax was a relative detractor, whose shares declined after KMX reported weaker-than-expected Q2 earnings that reflected economic pressures on vehicle sales.
